---
// Pure Minimal Testimonials Component
---

<section class="section testimonials-pure" id="testimonials">
	<div class="container-narrow">
		<div class="section-header scroll-reveal">
			<h2 class="section-title">What people are saying.</h2>
		</div>
		<div class="testimonials-grid">
			<div class="testimonial-pure scroll-reveal" style="animation-delay: 0s">
				<p class="testimonial-quote">
					"Luma gave me back hours of my day. I finally feel in control of my digital life."
				</p>
				<div class="testimonial-author">
					<span class="author-name">Sarah Chen</span>
					<span class="author-role">Product Designer, Stripe</span>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="testimonial-pure scroll-reveal" style="animation-delay: 0.1s">
				<p class="testimonial-quote">
					"The daily highlights alone are worth it. Luma is a game-changer for anyone managing multiple workspaces."
				</p>
				<div class="testimonial-author">
					<span class="author-name">Marcus Rodriguez</span>
					<span class="author-role">Engineering Lead, Notion</span>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="testimonial-pure scroll-reveal" style="animation-delay: 0.2s">
				<p class="testimonial-quote">
					"Finally, a messaging app that respects my attention. Open source + privacy-first is exactly what we needed."
				</p>
				<div class="testimonial-author">
					<span class="author-name">Emily Park</span>
					<span class="author-role">Founder, TechFlow</span>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="testimonial-pure scroll-reveal" style="animation-delay: 0.3s">
				<p class="testimonial-quote">
					"Switched to Luma 3 weeks ago. My screen time is down 40%. This is the future of messaging."
				</p>
				<div class="testimonial-author">
					<span class="author-name">Alex Kim</span>
					<span class="author-role">Software Engineer, Meta</span>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="testimonial-pure scroll-reveal" style="animation-delay: 0.4s">
				<p class="testimonial-quote">
					"The AI highlights are scary good. It knows what I need to see before I do. This is next-level."
				</p>
				<div class="testimonial-author">
					<span class="author-name">Jordan Smith</span>
					<span class="author-role">Designer, Figma</span>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="testimonial-pure scroll-reveal" style="animation-delay: 0.5s">
				<p class="testimonial-quote">
					"I've tried every productivity app. Luma is the only one that actually changed how I work."
				</p>
				<div class="testimonial-author">
					<span class="author-name">Taylor Wong</span>
					<span class="author-role">VP Product, Linear</span>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>

<style>
	.testimonials-pure {
		background: var(--gradient-subtle);
	}

	.testimonials-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
		gap: var(--spacing-lg);
		margin-top: var(--spacing-xl);
	}

	.testimonial-pure {
		background: white;
		border: 1px solid var(--color-border-light);
		border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
		padding: var(--spacing-xl);
		transition: all var(--transition-slow);
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: var(--spacing-md);
	}

	.testimonial-pure:hover {
		transform: translateY(-6px);
		box-shadow: var(--shadow-xl);
		border-color: var(--color-accent);
	}

	.testimonial-quote {
		font-size: 1.1875rem;
		line-height: 1.75;
		color: var(--color-text);
		font-style: italic;
		font-weight: 400;
		flex: 1;
	}

	.testimonial-quote::before {
		content: '"';
		color: var(--color-accent);
		font-size: 2rem;
		font-family: var(--font-serif);
		line-height: 0;
		vertical-align: -0.4rem;
		margin-right: 0.25rem;
	}

	.testimonial-author {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 0.25rem;
		padding-top: var(--spacing-sm);
		border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border-light);
	}

	.author-name {
		font-size: 0.9375rem;
		font-weight: 700;
		color: var(--color-text);
	}

	.author-role {
		font-size: 0.875rem;
		color: var(--color-text-light);
	}

	@media (max-width: 768px) {
		.testimonials-grid {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
		}

		.testimonial-pure {
			padding: var(--spacing-md);
		}

		.testimonial-quote {
			font-size: 1rem;
		}
	}
</style>

